@page "/markup-title"

<PageTitle>Verified — Public proof. €19/month.</PageTitle>

<h1>Markup-classified title test</h1>

<p>This page exists to pin Razor's source-generator behaviour for static
   title text containing non-ASCII characters (em-dash, euro sign). The
   transpiler test fixture derived from this page locks down whether the
   SG routes the content through <code>AddContent</code> or
   <code>AddMarkupContent</code> — the runtime's PageTitle has to handle
   both shapes either way.</p>
